      <title>THE CRAZY PROPOSITION</title>
      <author> Flygirlxoxox </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/2418448/the-crazy-proposition/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/2418448-the-crazy-proposition/chapter/2418451/#comments</comments>
